\c 130
\s Munyengetero wekukumbira kanganwiro nekununurwa
\d Rwiyo rwerwendo.
\p
\v 1 Ndakadanidzira kwamuri, Jehovha, ndiri muudziku.
\v 2 Ishe inzwai inzwi rangu; nzeve dzenyu ngadziteerere inzwi remikumbiro yangu.
\v 3 Dai imwi Jehovha, maicherekedza zvitadzo, ndiani angamira, Ishe?
\v 4 Asi kwamuri kune kanganwiro, kuti mutyiwe.
\p
\v 5 Ndakamirira Jehovha, mweya wangu unomirira; uye ndinotaririra shoko rake.
\v 6 Mweya wangu \add unorindira\add* Ishe, kupfuura kupfuura vanorindira rungwanani; vakarindira rungwanani.
\p
\v 7 Israeri ngaataririre kuna Jehovha, nokuti kuna Jehovha kune tsitsi, uye kwaari kune rudzikunuro rukuru.
\v 8 Zvino iye anodzikunura Israeri pazvitadzo zvake zvese.
